      "content": "self-care doesnt really change the fact that the world is hostile. i feel like no matter how much i \"rest\" or \"prioritize\" myself, i still have to wake up tomorrow and deal with the same rejection and the same feeling of being an outsider. it feels like a losing game. like, why am i even trying to win a game that was designed for me to fail?",
