    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "resistance feels so heavy. like i'm just fighting a tide that's never going to stop. i look at people who don't have to fight for every single inch of their identity and i just... i wonder what it would be like to not have to fight anymore. to just have peace. to just stop the noise. it feels like the only way to actually find peace is to just give up on all of this.",
